Again, I respect the bars dawg, but I just can't stand your annoying ass "listen to me right now!" ass voice and that goofy Simpsons character ass hair. There's not many people at all that urk me or bring hate outa me, but you do for some reason. I just can't watch another video of yours because if I do it might give me the urge to walk out on the street and murder a complete stranger.

And P.S. - Why tf you title every video "one take video" at the end ???

(Thats a rherorical question, bc 99.9% of people don't give .01% of half of a fuck that you shot the vid in one take 😖)
